search_results.title: Daniel Mason
search_results.snippet: Daniel Mason (born c. 1976) is an American novelist and physician. He is the author of The Piano Tuner, A Far Country and North Woods.

search_results.title: Matthew Mason - History
search_results.snippet: Matthew E. Mason is a professor of history at BYU. He received his PhD in history from the University of Maryland in 2002, and started at BYU in fall 2003.

search_results.title: Edward S. Mason
search_results.snippet: Edward Sagendorph Mason (February 22, 1899 – February 29, 1992) was an American economist and professor at Harvard University.
